<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10496482>
    dc:description "Fig.3. Variations in the corolla of Pteronia species studied.A – P.cederbergensis. B & C – P.aspera. D & E – P.camphorata. Vouchers:A – Levyn 5101 (BOL); B – Stokoe 17535 (BOL); C – Esterhuysen 22129 (BOL); D – Esterhuysen 13994 (BOL); E – Levyn 2324 (BOL). Scales: A, C–E = 1 mm, B = 0.5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10496482/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10496490>
    dc:description "Fig. 7. Morphology of Pteronia camphorata. A – flowering branch. B – cypselas (B1 – immature, B2 – mature). C – involucral bracts. D – style. E – floret, F – corolla. Vouchers: A–E – Oliver11134 (NBG), F – Esterhuysen 13994 (BOL).Scales: A = 2 cm, (B1, B2 & F) = 1 mm, C–E = 2 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10496490/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10496492>
    dc:description "Fig. 8. Known distribution of Pteronia camphorata." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10496492/files/figure.png" ;
